OL,3,CHealth secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,CPIP disability benefits U-turn
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, ITV News revealed that
OL,7,FLabour MPs had been called into No 10
OL,8,Ffor talks about major benefits cuts
OL,9,Fthat are expected to be announced
OL,10,Fearly next week.
OL,12,FAt least 80 of Starmer's MPs are
OL,13,Freported to oppose the benefits cuts
OL,14,Fand are said to be furious that a
OL,15,FLabour government is targeting some of
OL,16,Fthe most vulnerable in society.
OL,18,FThe radical package of reforms would
OL,19,Fsee:
