OL,6,FThe aim of the measures is to
OL,7,Fmassively increase the incentives for
OL,8,Fpeople to remain in the work-search
OL,9,Fcategory of Universal Credit, even if
OL,10,Fthey suffer with a health condition or
OL,11,Fdisability, but also to more than #6bn
OL,12,Fa year by the end of the decade.
OL,14,FWork and Pensions Secretary Liz
OL,15,FKendall is expected to announce
OL,16,Freforms on Tuesday aimed at cutting a
OL,17,Fwelfare bill that ministers have
OL,18,Fdescribed as "unsustainable".
