OL,3,CHealth secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,CPIP disability benefits U-turn
OL,6,FSomething's got to give, argues the
OL,7,Fgovernment, on welfare spending. The
OL,8,Fhealth and disability benefits bill
OL,9,Fhas been ballooning since Covid.
OL,11,FIt is forecast to rise from #64.7
OL,12,Fbillion in 2023-24 to #100.7 billion
OL,13,Fby 2029-30.
OL,15,FBefore the election the Sunak
OL,16,Fgovernment was going to change work
OL,17,Fcapability assessments to reflect the
OL,18,Ffact that working from home is now an
OL,19,Foption for more people.
