OL,3,CHealth secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,CPIP disability benefits U-turn
OL,6,FNow the Starmer government is planning
OL,7,Fto tighten up the eligibility for
OL,8,FPersonal Independence Payments (PIPs).
OL,10,FBut there was also a proposal on the
OL,11,Ftable to freeze PIPs next year instead
OL,12,Fof letting them rise in line with
OL,13,Finflation; a real terms cut.
OL,15,FLabour MPs visiting Downing Street in
OL,16,Fthe last week were presented with the
OL,17,Fbackdrop to these proposals but for
OL,18,Fmany of them it was clear that the
OL,19,Ffreezing of PIPs was a step too far.
